      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EPIFANIO (4) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing seventh (26.15) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Key player on best and worth another chance. QUICK BISCUIT (7) was resuming when finishing sixth at this track in a Mix 1/2/3 (20.43). Has a good record at this journey. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Better than last start and can bounce back. SHEEZEL (2) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.87 beating Big Easy Al. Draws to advantage and likes the trip. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. BACKCREEK BENNY (8) was below best last time at Taree Super Track (30.76) in a NG, finishing a 5.5 lengths sixth. Has six wins already from this draw.",
